metadata.name: Spirit of the Seas
metadata.description:
2000 × 1926 px 
00:06 (Loop)
24 fps

Spirit of the Seas depicts a female figure forming a spiritual link with nature, intertwined with the sky, the mountain and the sea. The art represents a subconscious interweaving ecosystem that has a life and energy of its own, depicting a surreal universe where imagination runs free from constraints of the rational mind.
